<svg viewBox="0 0 700 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
  <text x="20" y="28" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">3つの独立市場、同じ結論 — 大多数が損失を出す</text>
  <text x="20" y="46" fill="#9ca3af" font-size="11" font-family="sans-serif">損失または損益分岐点以下の口座比率・正確な数値は原資料を参照</text>
  <line x1="170" y1="90" x2="170" y2="350" stroke="#3f3f46" stroke-width="1"/>
  <line x1="290" y1="90" x2="290" y2="350" stroke="#27272a" stroke-width="1"/>
  <line x1="530" y1="90" x2="530" y2="350" stroke="#27272a" stroke-width="1"/>
  <line x1="650" y1="90" x2="650" y2="350" stroke="#27272a" stroke-width="1"/>
  <line x1="410" y1="90" x2="410" y2="350" stroke="#f7931a" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4,3"/>
  <text x="410" y="82" fill="#fbbf24" font-size="13" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif" text-anchor="middle">過半数(50%)</text>
